78
00:06:55,730 --> 00:06:56,660
will be doubled,

79
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,230
but I can't use other skills.

80
00:07:11,860 --> 00:07:13,160
But in the Berserker state,

81
00:07:13,500 --> 00:07:14,790
