113
00:08:45,900 --> 00:08:46,490
Xiang!

114
00:08:47,160 --> 00:08:48,790
I will protect you!

115
00:09:52,580 --> 00:10:02,110
[Soul Land]

116
00:10:39,860 --> 00:10:40,690
You're awake.

117
00:10:40,860 --> 00:10:42,060
That's great!

118
00:10:42,930 --> 00:10:44,060
Xiang.

119
00:10:47,930 --> 00:10:48,860
I'm sorry.

120
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,630
