122
00:10:51,930 --> 00:10:53,330
Why are you apologizing?

123
00:10:53,660 --> 00:10:55,160
This isn't your fault at all.

124
00:10:55,330 --> 00:10:56,860
It's all because I'm too weak

125
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,190
and dragged you all down.

126
00:10:58,300 --> 00:10:58,930
That's not it!

127
00:10:59,230 --> 00:11:01,060
If it hadn't been for you
fighting with the wolf thieves,

128
00:11:01,260 --> 00:11:02,590
those villagers would have been dead.

129
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:04,160
You saved them.

130
00:11:04,700 --> 00:11:05,460
Even if that's the case,

131
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:07,030
you still don't need to apologize to me.

132
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,330
Besides, you got wounded so badly

133
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:09,530
in order to save me.

134
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:13,930
I'm thick-skinned and not afraid of pain.

135
00:11:14,010 --> 00:11:15,250
You...

136
00:11:17,160 --> 00:11:20,190
It'll be bad if a weak girl like you gets hurt.

137
00:11:20,260 --> 00:11:21,560
Are you dumb?

138
00:11:21,930 --> 00:11:23,360
Who doesn't feel pain after getting hurt?

139
00:11:23,830 --> 00:11:26,030
