141
00:12:04,050 --> 00:12:04,550
Fatty.

142
00:12:05,180 --> 00:12:06,430
You really are dumb.

143
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:08,230
That's right.

144
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:10,630
A true dummy.

145
00:12:11,130 --> 00:12:13,160
